---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - The Centaur's Mind | Pragmatic Logic" description="Our mission to create emotionally intelligent AI that works in symbiosis with human ingenuity. Meet the team behind Lilo Solace and our vision for the future of healthcare AI.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>The Centaur's Mind</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Human Ingenuity and Artificial Intelligence working in perfect symbiosis‚Äîwhere emotional intelligence meets computational power to transform healthcare.
        </p>
        
        <div class="manifesto-preview">
          <blockquote>
            "The future of AI isn't about replacing human connection‚Äîit's about amplifying our capacity for empathy, understanding, and healing."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Centaur's Mind Manifesto -->
  <section class="manifesto-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="manifesto-content">
        <div class="manifesto-text">
          <h2>The Centaur's Mind Manifesto</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">Why Emotional Intelligence is the Missing Piece in Healthcare AI</p>
          
          <div class="manifesto-body">
            <h3>The Problem with Current AI</h3>
            <p>
              Today's healthcare AI excels at pattern recognition, data analysis, and clinical decision support. But it fundamentally lacks what makes healthcare truly healing: <strong>emotional intelligence</strong>. Patients don't just need accurate diagnoses‚Äîthey need to feel heard, understood, and cared for.
            </p>
            
            <h3>The Centaur Advantage</h3>
            <p>
              Like the mythical centaur that combines human intelligence with the strength of a horse, our approach combines human emotional wisdom with AI's computational power. This isn't about AI replacing healthcare workers‚Äîit's about creating a symbiotic relationship that amplifies both human empathy and artificial intelligence.
            </p>
            
            <h3>Emotional Intelligence in Action</h3>
            <p>
              Our multi-agent therapeutic AI system doesn't just process data‚Äîit recognizes emotional nuance, responds with appropriate empathy, and adapts its communication style to each individual's needs. This emotional intelligence is what transforms clinical interactions from transactional to transformational.
            </p>
            
            <div class="key-principles">
              <h3>Our Core Principles</h3>
              <div class="principles-grid">
                <div class="principle">
                  <div class="principle-icon">ü§ù</div>
                  <h4>Symbiosis Over Replacement</h4>
                  <p>AI should enhance human capabilities, not replace human connection</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="principle">
                  <div class="principle-icon">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>
                  <h4>Emotional Intelligence First</h4>
                  <p>Technical accuracy without empathy is insufficient for healing</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="principle">
                  <div class="principle-icon">üéØ</div>
                  <h4>Clinical-Grade Precision</h4>
                  <p>Emotional intelligence must be paired with clinical rigor</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="principle">
                  <div class="principle-icon">üîÑ</div>
                  <h4>Continuous Learning</h4>
                  <p>Both human and artificial intelligence must evolve together</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>The Future We're Building</h3>
            <p>
              We envision a healthcare system where AI doesn't just analyze symptoms‚Äîit understands the person behind them. Where technology doesn't create distance between caregiver and patient, but bridges it. Where artificial intelligence amplifies human compassion rather than replacing it.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              This is The Centaur's Mind: the perfect fusion of human emotional intelligence and artificial computational power, working together to heal not just bodies, but hearts and minds.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="manifesto-visual">
          <div class="centaur-diagram">
            <div class="diagram-title">The Centaur's Mind Model</div>
            <div class="centaur-parts">
              <div class="human-part">
                <h4>Human Intelligence</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Emotional Understanding</li>
                  <li>Empathetic Response</li>
                  <li>Cultural Sensitivity</li>
                  <li>Intuitive Judgment</li>
                  <li>Creative Problem-Solving</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-part">
                <h4>Artificial Intelligence</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Pattern Recognition</li>
                  <li>Data Processing</li>
                  <li>24/7 Availability</li>
                  <li>Consistent Quality</li>
                  <li>Scalable Delivery</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="symbiosis-result">
              <strong>= Emotionally Intelligent Healthcare AI</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            To create the world's first emotionally intelligent therapeutic AI platform that works in symbiosis with human caregivers, transforming senior mental health care through the perfect fusion of empathy and technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="vision-card">
          <h2>Our Vision</h2>
          <p>
            A future where every senior receives personalized, empathetic mental health support‚Äîwhere AI amplifies human compassion to prevent crises, reduce isolation, and restore dignity to aging.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Section -->
  <section class="founder-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Founder and Centaur Mindset</h2>
      <div class="founder-content">
        <div class="founder-image">
          <img src="/images/aejaz-profile.jpg" alt="Aejaz Sheriff Quaraishi, Founder & Principal Architect" class="profile-photo">
        </div>
        
        <div class="founder-info">
          <h3>Aejaz Sheriff Quaraishi</h3>
          <div class="founder-title">Founder & Principal Architect</div>
          
          <div class="founder-bio">
            <p>
              Accomplished Principal Enterprise & AI Architect with 28 years building regulated, mission-critical platforms across healthcare, AI, and IT/OT. Expert in microservices and interoperability (HL7 FHIR/PDex, CAQH, Epic, Availity), with deep RAG/agentic AI experience and robust evaluation frameworks.
            </p>
            
            <div class="founder-credentials">
              <h4>Background & Expertise</h4>
              <p><strong>Experience:</strong> 28+ years in enterprise architecture, AI/ML, and healthcare systems</p>
              <p><strong>Healthcare AI:</strong> Deep expertise in HIPAA-compliant platforms, HL7 FHIR, and clinical data interoperability</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="founder-achievements">
              <h4>Key Achievements at Pragmatic Logic</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Conceived and built clinical-grade, HIPAA-compliant therapeutic AI platform with 26 microservices</li>
                <li>Engineered 7-agent AI system achieving 100% recall and zero false negatives in crisis detection</li>
                <li>Established 7-dimension quality framework achieving 93.3/100 average response quality</li>
                <li>Delivered unified roadmap eliminating $1.75M‚Äì$2.55M in duplicate scope, 128 days ahead of plan</li>
                <li>Built RAG-based system unifying Knowledge Base, Life Story, and Consent frameworks</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="founder-motivation">
              <h4>Why Pragmatic Logic?</h4>
              <p>
                After nearly three decades in enterprise architecture and healthcare technology, I recognized a critical gap: AI systems that could process clinical data but couldn't truly understand the human experience. Having worked with major healthcare organizations like Blue Cross Blue Shield, I saw firsthand how technology often creates barriers between caregivers and patients rather than bridges.
              </p>
              <p>
                Pragmatic Logic represents my vision of The Centaur's Mind‚Äîwhere artificial intelligence doesn't replace human empathy but amplifies it. By combining my deep technical expertise in HIPAA-compliant systems, multi-agent architectures, and clinical interoperability with a profound understanding of what seniors and their families truly need, we're building AI that doesn't just analyze symptoms‚Äîit understands the person behind them.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
              <p><strong>Connect:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@pragmaticlogic.ai">contact@pragmaticlogic.ai</a> | <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/asheriff/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Values -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üß†</div>
          <h3>Clinical Excellence</h3>
          <p>Every decision is grounded in peer-reviewed research and clinical best practices</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üíù</div>
          <h3>Human-Centered Design</h3>
          <p>Technology should serve humanity, not the other way around</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üîí</div>
          <h3>Privacy & Security</h3>
          <p>Healthcare data deserves the highest levels of protection and respect</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>Ethical AI</h3>
          <p>AI development must be transparent, fair, and accountable</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üåü</div>
          <h3>Continuous Innovation</h3>
          <p>The pursuit of better outcomes never stops</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">ü§≤</div>
          <h3>Compassionate Care</h3>
          <p>Every interaction should leave people feeling more valued and understood</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Join Us in Building the Future</h2>
        <p>
          We're looking for investors, partners, and team members who share our vision of emotionally intelligent healthcare AI.
        </p>
        
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/demo" class="btn-primary-large">See Our Vision in Action</a>
          <a href="mailto:contact@pragmaticlogic.ai" class="btn-secondary-large">Join Our Mission</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #059669 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .manifesto-preview {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .manifesto-preview blockquote {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-style: italic;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border-left: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .manifesto-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
  }
  
  .manifesto-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  .manifesto-text h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .manifesto-body h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .manifesto-body p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .key-principles {
    background: white;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    margin: var(--space-8) 0;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .key-principles h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .principle {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .principle-icon {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .principle h4 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .principle p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .manifesto-visual {
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .centaur-diagram {
    background: white;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .diagram-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .centaur-parts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .human-part, .ai-part {
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .human-part {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
  }
  
  .ai-part {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }
  
  .human-part h4, .ai-part h4 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .human-part ul, .ai-part ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .human-part li, .ai-part li {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    padding: var(--space-1) 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }
  
  .symbiosis-result {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }
  
  .mission-section {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .mission-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .mission-card, .vision-card {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
  }
  
  .vision-card {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
  }
  
  .mission-card h2, .vision-card h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .mission-card p, .vision-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }
  
  .founder-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
  }
  
  .founder-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .founder-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  .founder-image {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .profile-photo {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    border: 4px solid white;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .profile-photo:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .image-placeholder {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    border: 2px dashed var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .placeholder-content {
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .placeholder-content h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .placeholder-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }
  
  .placeholder-content code {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: var(--space-1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .founder-info h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .founder-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .founder-bio p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .founder-credentials, .founder-achievements, .founder-motivation, .contact-info {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .founder-credentials h4, .founder-achievements h4, .founder-motivation h4 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .founder-credentials ul, .founder-achievements ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .founder-credentials li, .founder-achievements li {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  .founder-motivation p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .contact-info {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .values-section {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .values-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  
  .value-icon {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about-cta {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .about-cta h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .about-cta p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .btn-primary-large, .btn-secondary-large {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  
  .btn-primary-large {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .btn-primary-large:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary-large {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary-large:hover {
    border-color: white;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .manifesto-content,
    .mission-content,
    .founder-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
    
    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .profile-photo {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
